  "texts": [
    "Nevertheless, the computing power of ISAC systems can be limited, hindering the deployment of the large or complicated AI models.",
    "Apart from adopting the highperformance computing hardware, the novel computing frameworks, such as distributed computing [288] are expected to reduce the computing power requirement.",
    "On the one hand, distributed computing allows the distributed nodes to train and deploy AI model using their local data.",
    "On the other hand, distributed computing divides the AI model into several sub-models, which can be trained at different computing nodes parallelly.",
    "In addition, the effective computing power allocation is an important problem to be solved."
  ],
